  personSpokenTo: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 41f6666ec8adc1846b1cc0f2bf100762, type: 2}
  lines:
  - "You too man, my wife works at the orphanage I heard she\u2019s been volunteering
    at."
  - "All I hear is her praise, and good on you. It\u2019s tough raising a kid alone
    like that, the lower pay really sucks."
  - "And my condolences for your wife, losing her so early into your daughter\u2019s
    life, I could never imagine something so awful."
  bridgeAfterMessages: 1
  bridgeResponse1: Thank you, it means a lot.
